<table>
<tr>
<td width=240>
Doris Thurston&#8217;s simple cartoon-like drawings are delightful, her humor contagious. This first drawing captures the spirit 
of the Readers&#8217; Choice Awards, providing a sense of celebration.
</td>
<td width=100>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
<td align="right">
