We feel that the stark poignance of Christopher Patchel&#8217;s photograph evokes a sense of possibility as well as of loss, 
elements befitting Kay Anderson&#8217;s memorial.
</td>
<td width=124>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
<td align="right">
<img border="0" src="../../images/memorial_2007.jpg">
<br>Memorial:<br>Christopher Patchel<br>Chicago, Illinois
